  "init_eqs": "vol = 0; p1 = 0;\nvx = .2; vy = -0.1;\nkx = 0; ky = 0;\n",
  "frame_eqs": "dec_med = pow (0.96, 30/fps);\ndec_slow = pow (0.98, 30/fps);\nbeat = max (max (bass, mid), treb);\navg = avg*dec_slow + beat*(1-dec_slow);\nis_beat = above(beat, .5+avg+peak) * above (time, t0+.2);\nt0 = is_beat*time + (1-is_beat)*t0;\npeak = is_beat * beat + (1-is_beat)*peak*dec_med;\nindex = (index + is_beat) %8;\n\nq20 = avg;\nq21 = beat;\nq22 = peak;\nq23 = index;\nq24 = is_beat;\nvol = if (is_beat, vol*.8+.2*rand(100)/100, dec_med*vol);\n\np1 = .5 + .5*sin(time*.3);\nq26 = 0;\n\ntrig = is_beat && (rand(4)<2);\nkx = kx*(1-trig) + trig* (rand(100)/100-.5);\nky = ky*(1-trig) + trig* (rand(100)/100-.5);\nq10 = kx;\nq11 = ky;\n\ndo_once = if (below(do_once,1),1,0);\nxpos = do_once*xpos + (1-do_once)*xpos;\nypos = do_once*ypos + (1-do_once)*ypos;\n\n//xpos = xpos + .4*vol*sin(time*p1);\n//ypos = ypos + .4*vol*cos(time*p1);\n\nxpos = xpos + .05*vol;\nypos = ypos + .05*vy*vol;\n\nq12 = 10*sin(xpos);\nq13 = 10*cos(ypos);\nq14 = 10*sin(-xpos);\nq15 = 10*cos(ypos);\n\ntrig = is_beat && (rand(2)<1);\nvx = vx*(1-trig) + trig*(rand(10)-5)/10;\nvy = vy*(1-trig) + trig*(rand(10)-5)/10;\n\nq16 = 10*vx; // direction of light\nq17 = 10*vy;\n\nzoom = zoom + .3*vol;\nvy = vy + .2*vol;\n\nq18 = vol*.4; // brightness\n",
